        "template--19886097793322__9477cb49-16ee-4bcf-a04c-bf55ee8d3bc2-1688737592c993cae0-1": {
          "type": "press",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With a meticulous focus on functionality, durability, and style, they have managed to captivate the hearts of tech enthusiasts and professionals alike.</p>",
